# LMS Home Page Requirements

## Core Architecture
- The LMS Home Page must be part of a **Single Page Application (SPA)** architecture.
- Ensure the page loads dynamically without full browser refreshes.

## UI & Layout
- The home page layout must be completely **responsive**, optimizing seamlessly for mobile, tablet, and desktop views.
- Implement standard LMS landing sections (e.g., Hero banner, Featured Courses, Testimonials, and Footer).